#  Food Business Website

A modern, responsive **Food Business Web Application** built with **React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and React Query**.
This project provides a clean menu browsing experience for customers and a powerful admin panel to manage products.

---

##  Live Features

###  Customer Side

* Browse food menu by categories
* View dish prices, descriptions, and tags
* Responsive design for mobile, tablet & desktop

###  Admin Panel

* Add new food items
* Edit existing products
* Delete products
* Manage prices, categories, images, and stock

