##  How to Run Locally

### 1️ Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 2️ Start the app

```bash
npm run dev
```

Open in browser:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

##  Admin Access

The Admin Panel is protected using an **AdminGuard**.
Only authorized users can access product management.



